e":202},{"type":14,"tag":234,"props":815,"children":816},{},[817],{"type":25,"value":818},"Transport your data to suit a wide range of applications. Enables utilities to reduce operating costs by efficiently managing binary data, leading to lower storage, bandwidth, and maintenance expenses, ultimately enhancing cost-effectiveness in the utility sector.",{"type":25,"value":782},{"type":25,"value":196},{"type":14,"tag":198,"props":822,"children":823},{},[824,825,840,841,851,852,857],{"type":25,"value":202},{"type":14,"tag":234,"props":826,"children":827},{},[828,830,833,834],{"type":25,"value":829},"LTE-MTC Band Config ",{"type":14,"tag":680,"props":831,"children":832},{},[],{"type":25,"value":684},{"type":14,"tag":28,"props":835,"children":837},{"href":836,"target":30},"http://devtoolkit.openmobilealliance.org/OEditor/LWMOView?url=https%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2FOpenMobileAlliance%2Flwm2m-registry%2Fprod%2F501.xml",[838],{"type":25,"value":839},"#501",{"type":25,"value":202},{"type":14,"tag":234,"props":842,"children":843},{},[844,849],{"type":14,"tag":453,"props":845,"children":846},{},[847],{"type":25,"value":848},"LTE Band Configuration",{"type":25,"value":850},": Allows to fine tune the LTE connectivity parameter. It is used to configure the cellular band used by the device as well as to change the band. It is intended to be used on LTE bands, as in NB-IoT and LTE Cat M1 frequency bands.",{"type":25,"value":202},{"type":14,"tag":234,"props":853,"children":854},{},[855],{"type":25,"value":856},"Construct the optimal power budget for the device's lifespan and adjust to evolving situations. This object empowers utilities to make informed choices about their IoT device communication, leading to reduced operating costs through enhanced efficiency, reduced manual intervention, and improved data quality. It aligns with the industry's goal of optimizing operations while maintaining reliable service delivery.",{"type":25,"value":782},{"type":25,"value":196},{"type":14,"tag":198,"props":860,"children":861},{},[862,863,874,875,885,886,891],{"type":25,"value":257},{"type":14,"tag":234,"props":864,"children":865},{},[866,868],{"type":25,"value":867},"Remote SIM Prov. ObjID: ",{"type":14,"tag":28,"props":869,"children":871},{"href":870,"target":30},"http://devtoolkit.openmobilealliance.org/OEditor/LWMOView?url=https%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2FOpenMobileAlliance%2Flwm2m-registry%2Fprod%2F504.xml",[872],{"type":25,"value":873},"#504",{"type":25,"value":257},{"type":14,"tag":234,"props":876,"children":877},{},[878,883],{"type":14,"tag":453,"props":879,"children":880},{},[881],{"type":25,"value":882},"Remote SIM Provisioning",{"type":25,"value":884},": Facilitates remote SIM profile updates, supports network migration, remove risk of stranded assets.",{"type":25,"value":257},{"type":14,"tag":234,"props":887,"children":888},{},[889],{"type":25,"value":890},"Enables the choice of the most optimal networks, switching as better options become available or prioritizing those with the lowest power consumption to benefit the device's lifespan. It empowers utilities to streamline SIM card management, optimize network usage, enhance security, and reduce downtime.",{"type":25,"value":196},{"type":25,"value":190},{"type":25,"value":894},"\n ",{"type":14,"tag":63,"props":896,"children":898},{"id":897},"conclusion",[899],{"type":25,"value":900},"Conclusion:",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":902,"children":903},{},[904],{"type":25,"value":905},"In the ever-evolving landscape of utility management, the efficient and secure management of electricity meters is of utmost importance. This document has shed light on how the LightweightM2M (LwM2M) protocol serves as the ideal solution by effectively addressing utility pain points, enhancing security, and reducing operating costs, all while streamlining the management of utility applications.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":907,"children":908},{},[909],{"type":25,"value":910},"We've explored how LwM2M offers robust solutions for secure device management, connectivity monitoring, and compliance, ensuring the resilience and effectiveness of utility management systems. Additionally, we've delved into LwM2M's services, demonstrating how they can significantly lower operating costs by automating tasks, enhancing security, and offering proactive insights.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":912,"children":913},{},[914],{"type":25,"value":915},"Furthermore, the document has showcased LwM2M's range of Object IDs, each tailored to enhance operational efficiency and reduce costs for utility organizations. From ensuring device authenticity to optimizing network usage, these Object IDs empower utilities to proactively manage their assets, minimize downtime, and make informed choices, ultimately contributing to substantial cost savings.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":917,"children":918},{},[919],{"type":25,"value":920},"In summary, LwM2M is revolutionizing smart meter management in the utility sector, offering unprecedented efficiency, security, and cost-effectiveness. Embracing this protocol can unlock substantial savings while ensuring the reliability and excellence of utility services.",{"title":5,"searchDepth":47,"depth":47,"links":922},[923,924,925,931],{"id":65,"depth":47,"text":68},{"id":90,"depth":47,"text":93},{"id":164,"depth":47,"text":167,"children":926},[927,929,930],{"id":176,"depth":928,"text":179},3,{"id":394,"depth":928,"text":397},{"id":581,"depth":928,"text":584},{"id":897,"depth":47,"text":900},"content:4.utilities:20.market-potential:20.whitepaper-lwm2m-metering-use-case.md","4.utilities/20.market-potential/20.whitepaper-lwm2m-metering-use-case.md",[935],{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":7,"description":8,"visible":9,"body":936,"_type":49,"_id":50,"_source":51,"_file":52,"_extension":53},{"type":11,"children":937,"toc":953},[938],{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":939,"children":940},{},[941],{"type":14,"tag":19,"props":942,"children":944},